room_title: Escape room "The Collection" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
room_address: 114 Broadway N Suite L1 Fargo, ND 58102
room_description: It's been almost 100 years and no one has solved The Collection, a thirteen piece set of cryptic artwork by renowned artists Alexander & Andrea van Housen who are thought to be haunting it. You have been invited to a private showing at 11 pm on the eve of The Collection's 100 year anniversary. Can you solve the art before the clock strikes midnight and the artists return from the dead with a vengeance?
